name: Jenkins - Job Overview
description: The Jenkins - Job Overview dashboard provides a high-level view of job status, trends, comparisons, and results.

panels.name: Successful Builds
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "label", "result" as Name, Label, Result
| where Result matches "SUCCESS"
| count as Success

panels.name: Total Builds
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "label", "result" as Name, Label, Result
| count as TotalBuilds

panels.name: Recent Builds
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobRunDuration", "number", "result", "name", "jobBuildURL", "label" as Duration, Number, Result, Name, URL, Label nodrop
| _sourceHost as Master
| tourl(URL, Name) as Name
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", ":white-heavy-check-mark:", ":prohibited:") as icon
| lookup utf as Result from https://s3.amazonaws.com/sumologic-app-data/emoji.csv on shortname=icon
| count by Master, Name, Number, Result, Label, _messageTime
| sort by _messageTime
| fields - _count, _messageTime

panels.name: Jobs by Node Name
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "nodeName", "name", "number", "label", "result" as %"Node Name", Name, Number, Label, Result
| count by %"Node Name", Name
| transpose row %"Node Name" column Name

panels.name: Job Result Trend
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "number","label", "result" as Name, Number, Label, Result nodrop
| timeslice 10m
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", "Success", "Failure") as Result
| count by _timeslice, Result
| transpose row _timeslice column Result
| fillmissing timeslice(10m)

panels.name: Jobs in Queue
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Queue_Event
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobName" as Name
| first(_raw) by Name, Master
| json field = _first "queueId", "queueTime", "isBlocked", "reasonForBlock", "isConcurrentBuild", "jobName", "jobURL" as %"Queue Id", %"Queue Time(sec)", Blocked, Reason, %"Concurrent Build", Name, URL nodrop
| tourl(URL, Name) as Name
| replace (URL, /\/[0-9]{1,}/, "") as URL
| where ![subquery : $$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobBuildURL" as URL
| replace (URL, /\/[0-9]{1,}/, "") as URL
| count by URL, Master
| compose URL, Master]
| count by Master, %"Queue Id", %"Queue Time(sec)", Name, Blocked, Reason, %"Concurrent Build"
| fields - _count

panels.name: Jobs Average Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name","number","label","jobRunDuration", "result" as Name, Number, Label, Duration, Result
| Duration/60 as Duration
| timeslice 10m
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by _timeslice
| fillmissing timeslice(10m)
| outlier %"Duration in minutes"

panels.name: Job Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobRunDuration", "number", "result", "name", "label" as Duration, Number, Result, Name, Label nodrop
| concat(Name,"#" ,Number) as Name
| Duration/60 as Duration
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by Name, _messageTime
| sort by _messageTime asc
| fields - _messageTime

panels.name: Compare Result (Current / 1 day compare)
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "label","result", "jobRunDuration" as Name,Label, Result, Duration
| count by Name, Result, Master
| transpose row Name, Master column Result as %"SUCCESS", %"FAILURE", %"ABORTED", %"UNSTABLE"
| compare with timeshift 1d
| concat(if(isNull(SUCCESS), tolong(0), SUCCESS), " / ", if(isNull(SUCCESS_1d), tolong(0), SUCCESS_1d)) as %"Compare Success"
| concat(if(isNull(FAILURE), tolong(0), FAILURE), " / ", if(isNull(FAILURE_1d), tolong(0), FAILURE_1d)) as %"Compare Failure"
| concat(if(isNull(ABORTED), tolong(0), ABORTED), " / ", if(isNull(ABORTED_1d), tolong(0), ABORTED_1d)) as %"Compare Aborted"
| concat(if(isNull(UNSTABLE), tolong(0), UNSTABLE), " / ", if(isNull(UNSTABLE_1d), tolong(0), UNSTABLE_1d)) as %"Compare Unstable"
| fields Master, Name, %"Compare Success", %"Compare Failure", %"Compare Aborted", %"Compare Unstable"

panels.name: Top 10 Slowest Failed Jobs
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "result", "label", "jobRunDuration" as Name, Result, Label, Duration
| where !(Result matches "SUCCESS")
| Duration/60 as Duration
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by Name, Duration
| sort by %"Duration in minutes"
| fields - Duration
| limit 10

panels.name: Failed Builds
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "label", "result" as Name, Label, Result
| where !(Result matches "SUCCESS")
| count as Failures

panels.name: Top 10 Slowest Successful Jobs(Minutes)
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "result", "jobRunDuration", "label" as Name, Result, Duration, Label
| where Result matches "SUCCESS"
| Duration/60 as Duration
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by Duration, Name
| sort by %"Duration in minutes"
| fields - Duration
| limit 10

panels.name: Jobs Status Percentage
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name","label","result" as Name, Label, Result
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", 1, 0) as Success
| if(Result matches "FAILURE", 1, 0) as Failure
| if(Result matches "ABORTED", 1, 0) as Aborted
| if(Result matches "UNSTABLE", 1, 0) as Unstable
| timeslice 30m
| count as Total_Logs, sum(Success) as Successes, sum(Failure) as Failures, sum(Aborted) as Abort, sum(Unstable) as Unstable by _timeslice
| (Successes/Total_Logs) as Successful
| (Failures/Total_Logs) as Failed
| (Abort/Total_Logs) as Aborted
| (Unstable/Total_Logs) as Unstable
| fields _timeslice, Successful, Failed, Aborted, Unstable

panels.name: Max Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "label", "result", "jobRunDuration" as Name, Label, Result, Duration
| Duration/60 as Duration
| max(Duration)

panels.name: Jobs in Progress
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc In_Progress
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "result", "number" as Name, Result, Number
| where Result = "In_Progress"
| first(_raw) by Name, Number, Master
| json field=_first "jobBuildURL", "label", "nodeName", "jobStartTime", "jobRunDuration" as URL, Label, %"Node Name", %"Start Time", %"Duration(sec)" nodrop
| where ![subquery : $$jenkinslogsrc "logType":"Job_Status"
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "number" as Name, Number
| count by Master, Name, Number   
| compose Master, Name, Number]  
| tourl(URL, Name) as Name
| count by Master, Name, Label, %"Node Name", %"Start Time", %"Duration(sec)", Number
| fields Master, Name, Label, %"Node Name", %"Start Time", %"Duration(sec)", Number
